cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.NE

The paper deals with object detection and localization in compressed video frames, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of compressive sensing also involves signal processing (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT). The proposed model for object detection and localization is based on deep learning, which is a popular topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE).
